import jxl.*
def NumOfXLSRows
def XLPath = testRunner.testCase.testSuite.project.getPropertyValue("XLPath1")
log.info ("Path : " + XLPath)
Workbook objWB = Workbook.getWorkbook(new File(XLPath)) Sheet objSheet = objWB.getSheet(0) NumOfXLSRows = objSheet.getRows()
log.info ("Number of TZ_Xls rows: " + NumOfXLSRows)
version = objSheet.getCell(8,2).getContents() discipline = objSheet.getCell(9,2).getContents()
log.info("version_Value: " + version) log.info("discipline_Value: " + discipline)
testRunner.testCase.setPropertyValue("version", version) testRunner.testCase.setPropertyValue("discipline", discipline)
objWB.close()
